snippet.title: Best VGM 1675 - Mario & Luigi : Superstar Saga - Hoohoo Village
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 55 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2BNMm9irLTw

A collection of my favorite videogame musics. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

GBA
Mario & Luigi : Superstar Saga (2003)
Hoohoo Village
Yoko Shimomura
